ida-adreno-qrisc is maintained by the adreno-qrisc contributors.

Upstream attribution
====================

The ISA, PM4 packet definitions, control-register layout, and reference
disassembler this project validates against were authored by the freedreno
contributors to Mesa 3D — in particular the qrisc/afuc subsystem, originally
by Rob Clark (Red Hat / Google), with substantial later work by Connor Abbott
(Valve) and other Mesa contributors. See:

  https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/mesa/mesa/-/tree/main/src/freedreno/qrisc

Mesa is MIT-licensed; copyright remains with the respective Mesa authors.
See NOTICE.

